ParticipantID: ID number of participant (may repeat depending if they provide primary/secondary or current/past configs)
Name: Participant Name
Current/Past: Current (2020/2021) or past (last 5 years) gear configuration
GillnetType: Type of gillnet fished (Anchored Sink/Float/Drift/Tended Bait)
Panels/String: Number of panels in the string
Scope: Scope of Vertical Line to Depth (fathoms)
Splice/KnotType: Type of knot or splice used
Daytrip/Overnight: If the gear configuration is fished as a daytrip, overnight, or both
Days/Season: Numbers of Days fished per season
